{"tid":2167883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓投資者蜂擁進入中國股市，金額較去年同期增長約7倍，創有史以​​來最大規模","createTime":"2020-08-21T11:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T13:05:04.000Z","uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6dd3ca9589937b8f2daa063ba4a9856be3bb02de","tid":2167883,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"南韓的家庭主婦等散戶向來樂於在投資上冒險，而據南韓證券集中保管公司（Korea Securities Depository，KSD）數據，南韓散戶僅是在7月，就斥資2.4億美元（約新台幣71億元）購買中國股票，和去年同期的3290萬美元相比約大漲7倍，創南韓投資者投資中國股市有史以​​來最大規模，投資對象則多為中國科技股，此現象的背後原因，則可能來自南韓當局嚴格規範房產抵押、擬對股票投資者加徵資本利得稅 （Capital gains tax），和南韓散戶看準中國推動科技自主所致。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》今（21）報導，KSD數據顯示，南韓投資者今年7月購買了價值約2.4億美元的中國股票，約佔該國1至7月對中國股票淨投資額（7.19億美元）的1/3。<br />\n<br />\n另據KSD數據，南韓投資者在1至7月主要購買的10家中企股票中，有6家是科技公司，這6檔股票的漲幅從年初至今，平均約高達32％，而三星電子和SK海力士的股價，同期則約分別下跌0.7％和23.7％。6擋股票中，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">南韓投資者對華為供應商「深南電路」（Shennan Circuit Company Limited）的淨投資額最高，達5536萬美元，其他如中興通訊、浪潮電子資訊公司（Inspur Electronic Information Technology Co Ltd）、上海韋爾半導體（Will Semiconductor Co）和立訊精密（Luxshare Precision）也都榜上有名。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n據報導，南韓散戶可能因南韓當局對房產抵押的限制，和打算擴大對股票投資者的資本利得稅，而轉向國外尋找投資標的，導致對中國股市的投資增加；<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>一位Kim姓南韓主廚則受訪表示，自己因看上中國在美中貿易戰下推動科技產業自給自足，而投資中國股市，並透露自己在中國股票上的投資，約達近5億美元。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nKim指出，南韓散戶對中國股票的興趣和過去相比，確實大幅增加，而南韓當局對該國股市的嚴格監管，以及中國股市出現2015年以來前所未見的繁榮，可能是背後原因。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3267248\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3267248&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=1c1241da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3267248&h=ee6256c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3267248</a>"},{"pid":"9b1708d9acc136ac15b2d406494f6a21b01d2397","tid":2167883,"uid":185100,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"廚師股票有五億美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81c037a6baf6fa39bcb472cce72f29fd1689b2f","tid":2167883,"uid":13663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:43:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔＞買tsla <br />\n泡菜仔＞買華為中芯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e3574b2bbc9323b2472a23a5b13076d124c45a","tid":2167883,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:45:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ace2a841dc0f07d02b1df24f3101730936d0d02","tid":2167883,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"撤薩德啦"},{"pid":"a188e396a75ddeb99499b1ee2f28b71d2f296735","tid":2167883,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:48:13.000Z","msg":"有5億美金都要做廚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a11aacedaeab0bfbcfa9e9306380084c2bc252","tid":2167883,"uid":75656,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T11:56:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-southkorea-investors-china/stymied-at-home-koreas-mom-and-pop-investors-charge-into-china-tech-stocks-idUSKBN25H0D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-southkorea-investors-china%2Fstymied-at-home-koreas-mom-and-pop-investors-charge-into-china-tech-stocks-idUSKBN25H0D1&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=1399524a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-southkorea-investors-china%2Fstymied-at-home-koreas-mom-and-pop-investors-charge-into-china-tech-stocks-idUSKBN25H0D1&h=13bb6a41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-southkorea-investors-china/stymied-at-home-koreas-mom-and-pop-investors-charge-into-china-tech-stocks-idUSKBN25H0D1</a><br />\n<br />\nAmon